The classes under org.pitest.mutationtest.history are derived from the
default history implementation present in pitest up to and including
version 1.16.3, which was removed from pitest core in commit 1b87fddb1d70
("remove default history analysis"). This project re-packages those
classes as a standalone plugin for current pitest versions.
